802
01:20:23,874 --> 01:20:27,001
a 59-year-old man
named Herbert Karlsson.

803
01:20:27,168 --> 01:20:30,504
No word yet on whether or not...

804
01:20:30,671 --> 01:20:33,090
You work
at the dentist's, right?

805
01:20:33,257 --> 01:20:35,175
Yeah.

806
01:20:35,342 --> 01:20:38,053
I'm Annie.
I used to go there.

807
01:20:38,219 --> 01:20:41,181
- OK.
- I was at Chris's birthday party.

808
01:20:41,348 --> 01:20:43,099
Everything went totally crazy.
And I can't find anybody.

809
01:20:43,265 --> 01:20:45,809
And my mom dropped me off,
and I don't know where she is.

810
01:20:45,976 --> 01:20:48,520
I saw you, and I remembered
that you used to be really nice,

811
01:20:48,687 --> 01:20:50,064
even though the dentist
was kinda scary.

812
01:20:50,230 --> 01:20:53,483
You used to call him chrome dome
when he left the room.

813
01:20:53,650 --> 01:20:55,443
Uh-huh.

814
01:20:55,610 --> 01:20:57,195
Can you drive me home?

815
01:20:57,362 --> 01:20:59,280
I'm scared.

816
01:21:01,324 --> 01:21:03,575
You want a ride home?

817
01:21:03,742 --> 01:21:06,745
Please.
I don't know anyone else.

818
01:21:12,792 --> 01:21:14,877
You're so nice.

819
01:21:43,152 --> 01:21:45,071
Sorry I don't know the way.

820
01:21:45,238 --> 01:21:47,615
Oh, it's alright.
We'll... I know your street.

821
01:21:47,781 --> 01:21:49,825
So we'll find your house.
Don't worry.

822
01:21:49,991 --> 01:21:51,410
You're so nice.

823
01:21:51,576 --> 01:21:53,745
Well, you...

824
01:21:53,912 --> 01:21:57,456
You know, I...think
if it were my son in trouble,

825
01:21:57,623 --> 01:22:01,711
I'd wish someone
would help him out, so...

826
01:23:08,896 --> 01:23:10,272
Are we here?

827
01:23:10,439 --> 01:23:12,356
Yeah. This is it.

828
01:23:13,983 --> 01:23:15,693
You're home.

829
01:23:24,367 --> 01:23:25,827
This isn't...

830
01:23:31,624 --> 01:23:33,292
This isn't my house.

831
01:23:34,376 --> 01:23:35,920
This isn't my house!

832
01:23:38,339 --> 01:23:42,133
Hey, it's scary out here.
Unlock it, please!

833
01:23:45,303 --> 01:23:47,930
Please. Unlock it, please.

834
01:23:50,599 --> 01:23:52,017
There's someone out here.

835
01:23:52,184 --> 01:23:54,645
Please. Please unlock the door.

836
01:23:54,812 --> 01:23:57,188
Please! PLEASE!

837
01:23:57,355 --> 01:23:59,690
There's someone out here.
Please unlock the door!

838
01:23:59,857 --> 01:24:01,776
Please unlock it!

839
01:24:01,943 --> 01:24:04,195
Unlock the door, please!

840
01:24:04,362 --> 01:24:06,571
Unlock it, please!

841
01:24:11,576 --> 01:24:13,870
Please!

842
01:24:14,037 --> 01:24:16,372
Get in the car! I'm sorry.

843
01:24:16,539 --> 01:24:19,208
- What are you doing?
- I'm so sorry.

844
01:24:19,375 --> 01:24:21,126
It's not safe out there!

845
01:24:21,293 --> 01:24:23,087
Hey!

846
01:24:23,254 --> 01:24:24,796
No.

847
01:24:28,049 --> 01:24:30,343
Hey. Wait here.

848
01:24:41,019 --> 01:24:42,396
Jack.

849
01:24:46,858 --> 01:24:48,943
Dad, call me back.

850
01:24:49,110 --> 01:24:50,486
OK?

851
01:24:50,653 --> 01:24:52,238
Where are you and Jack?

852
01:24:54,447 --> 01:24:56,533
Home at last.

853
01:24:58,493 --> 01:25:01,162
OK, let's go and have
a little chat with your dad.

854
01:25:04,832 --> 01:25:06,959
Stay close to Grandpa.

855
01:25:46,912 --> 01:25:49,705
Dad! I told you
not to come back here.

856
01:25:49,872 --> 01:25:51,582
- Where's Jack?
- He's OK.

857
01:25:51,749 --> 01:25:53,125
He's up in his room.

858
01:25:53,292 --> 01:25:55,461
Dad, I made a...
I made a mistake.

859
01:25:55,628 --> 01:25:57,170
Listen. I don't know
what happened.

860
01:25:57,337 --> 01:25:58,713
I don't care what happened.

861
01:25:58,880 --> 01:26:00,715
I just don't want you
implicated in this.

862
01:26:00,882 --> 01:26:04,010
Whatever Kent did, it's OK.
I'm gonna help you, OK?

863
01:26:04,177 --> 01:26:05,803
I'm gonna help you.

864
01:26:07,179 --> 01:26:09,222
What are you talking about?

865
01:26:09,389 --> 01:26:11,683
I'll clean up the blood.

866
01:26:11,850 --> 01:26:13,560
No-one'll know.

867
01:26:13,727 --> 01:26:17,021
Baby, you're my little girl.
I love you.

868
01:26:17,188 --> 01:26:19,857
I...

869
01:26:30,075 --> 01:26:34,912
One...child...more!

870
01:26:37,790 --> 01:26:39,333
Ah!

871
01:28:03,408 --> 01:28:05,326
Run, Jack!

872
01:28:05,493 --> 01:28:07,578
Jack!

873
01:28:34,393 --> 01:28:36,145
Clown motherfucker!

874
01:28:40,191 --> 01:28:42,610
Arggh!

875
01:28:42,777 --> 01:28:44,402
Ahh!

876
01:31:48,233 --> 01:31:49,943
Mom?

877
01:31:50,109 --> 01:31:51,778
Don't watch, Jack.

878
01:31:51,945 --> 01:31:53,821
OK, we got him.

879
01:31:56,157 --> 01:31:58,033
Meg...

880
01:32:02,788 --> 01:32:04,539
..help me.

881
01:32:07,833 --> 01:32:09,335
We got him.

882
01:32:09,502 --> 01:32:11,045
Jack?

883
01:32:12,129 --> 01:32:14,966
Jack. Go get that book.

884
01:32:15,132 --> 01:32:17,342
What?

885
01:32:17,509 --> 01:32:20,178
