886
01:32:20,345 --> 01:32:22,430
And...and go get more chains.

887
01:32:22,597 --> 01:32:24,516
Why?

888
01:32:24,683 --> 01:32:26,767
Don't you wanna help Daddy?

889
01:32:26,934 --> 01:32:29,645
That's not Daddy.

890
01:32:59,797 --> 01:33:01,756
Jack, I'm sorry.

891
01:33:01,923 --> 01:33:04,426
I'm so sorry.

892
01:33:16,687 --> 01:33:18,355
Ugh! Ugh!

893
01:33:49,674 --> 01:33:52,010
Mom.
